Usage: infinit-credentials credentials [MODE|--help]
Infinit credentials management utility.

Modes:
  add        Add credentials for a third-party service
  delete     Delete locally credentials for a third-party service
  fetch      Fetch credentials from https://beyond.infinit.sh
  pull       Pull credentials from https://beyond.infinit.sh
  list       List local credentials

Options:
  -h, --help                show this help message

